text:'{"blocks":[{"key":"5dfgs","text":"Weeds are not just unsightly in the garden, they can also damage your plants and parasitic weeds can certainly kill them. Mulching provides a layer on top of the soil, which makes it harder for weeds to break through in order to grow. The extra layer also provides another barrier that stops sunlight from reaching the open spaces in which weeds thrive.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"textShadowBlur:8px"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"WebkitTextStrokeWidth:1px"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"fontStyle:normal"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"defaultTextStrokeWidth:1px"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"WebkitTextStrokeColor:#ffffff"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"hlnkt:wp"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"fontWeight:400"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"textOutlineEnable:false"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"opacity:1"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"hlnke:true"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"defaultTextShadow:none"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"backgroundColor:unset"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"textShadow:none"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"defaultTextStrokeColor:#ffffff"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"fontFamily:Rosario"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"textShadowX:0px"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"fontStretch:normal"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"fontType:regular"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"defaultBackgroundColor:#E8D01B"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"textShadowY:4px"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"textShadowColor:#F1EEE61F"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"letterSpacing:0%"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"textHighlightEnable:false"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"textTransform:none"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"textShadowOpacity:none"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"textDecoration:none"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"lineHeight:130%"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"borderBottomStyle:none"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"textShadowEnable:false"},{"offset":0,"length":353,"style":"hlnk:"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"listDepth":"0","listColor":"#666666","verticalAlignMarginBottom":"40px","listIndent":"100%","overridden":"false","marginLeft":"0px","verticalAlignMarginTop":"auto","listType":"S_Bullets08","textAlign":"left","marginBottom":"40%","presetId":"text-body-1","listSize":"100%"}},{"key":"f25gr","text":"\\nWide areas are notoriously popular with weed growth, and this is because open spaces allow them to drop seeds and germinate into the soil easily. Mulching deprives weeds of bare ground, which means that the seeds never get the opportunity to touch the soil. Weeds seeds can range from 200 to 54,000 seeds per square foot of so1l.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"fontStyle:normal"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"defaultTextStrokeWidth:1px"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"WebkitTextStrokeColor:#ffffff"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"hlnkt:wp"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"fontWeight:400"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"textOutlineEnable:false"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"opacity:1"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"hlnke:true"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"defaultTextShadow:none"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"backgroundColor:unset"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"textShadow:none"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"defaultTextStrokeColor:#ffffff"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"fontFamily:Rosario"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"textShadowX:0px"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"fontStretch:normal"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"fontType:regular"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"defaultBackgroundColor:#E8D01B"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"textShadowY:4px"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"textShadowColor:#F1EEE61F"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"letterSpacing:0%"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"textHighlightEnable:false"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"textTransform:none"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"textShadowOpacity:none"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"textDecoration:none"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"lineHeight:130%"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"borderBottomStyle:none"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"textShadowEnable:false"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"hlnk:"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"textShadowBlur:8px"},{"offset":0,"length":330,"style":"WebkitTextStrokeWidth:1px"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{"listDepth":"0","listColor":"#666666","listIndent":"100%","overridden":"false","marginLeft":"0px","listType":"S_Bullets08","textAlign":"left","marginBottom":"40%","presetId":"text-body-1","listSize":"100%"}}],"entityMap":{}}',
